name: Tailored Egos Tee
description: Basic white tee. Suttle, yet so bold. Stand out, & tell people how you do it with the Tailored Egos  OG white Tee.

name: Air Jordan 12 " Taxi "
description: This AJ12 caused quite the frenzy the last time they were released as part of the Jordan 11 and Jordan 12 Collezione Package back in 2008. This time around this original black and white colorway adds a bit of an extra gold look to its eyelets. These wont last long. *Ships on release date*

name: Nike Lebron 11 " Miami Nights "
description: The sneaker community got a chance to see another Player Exclusive colorway of a LeBron model on court Tuesday night as James laced up his "Ring Ceremony" LeBron 11's for opening night in the NBA. While the general public won't be able to get their hands on those, more from James' eleventh signature series is on the way such as the "Miami Nights" edition which we get another look at above. Featuring a mostly black/carbon fiber build, this design is set off by pink accents on the Dynamic Flywire and tongue lining.*Ships on release date*

name: Nike KD 6 " Rugrats"
description: It seems that the KD 6 will continue to make reference to Durant’s childhood with this upcoming “Rugrats” colorway. The sneakers feature a bright leaning colorway across the top along with some shapes on the innards that would like right at home in that classic Nickelodeon show. See some more angles on the purported KD 6 “Rugrats” with us after the break and stay tuned for updates on these and more Kevin Durant shoes.* Ships on release date*

name: Nike Kobe 4 " Venomenon "
description: This month just might mark the busiest one ever for Nike Kobe shoes. Not only is the Kobe 8 still ticking, but there are also the retros from the Prelude Pack and this, the Nike Zoom Kobe 4 blazing out the gates with this black based colorway that comes complete with a glowing sole on bottom.

name: The Sole Collector x Nike Air Zoom Flight " The Glove "
description: Straight FIRE. Beautiful collab between Sole Collector & Nike

name: Timberland " Cognac Brown "
description: This new color way is in right in time for winter. Dark in color and rich in quality is the Timberland " Cognac Brown" . Take a step out of sneakers and get a pair of these. * Ships immediately *

name: Timberland " Black " gs
description: Gradeschool sizes only until further notice

name: Air Jordan V Retro " Oreo "
description: It’s a huge year for the Air Jordan 5 – 2013 marks the 23rd anniversary of the classic silhouette, a significant milestone because it’s the number of the beast, Mr J himself. Jordan Brand has a swag of new colourways set to drop over the year, and this ‘Oreo’ flip is sure to hit big with heads come its expected Black Friday drop date. There are some dope details at play on this Jordan too, a black suede upper plays off nicely against the bright white midsole and white lining, with a speckled black teeth pattern the centre piece of this mean machine.

name: Nike Penny V " camo "
description: Hot on the heels of the “Lil Penny” colorway comes this “Camo” version of the Air Penny V from Nike. The shoe features a leather and synthetics build with camo featured on the eystays, collar and midsole, with black leather, mesh and synthetics taking over the rest of the design. Bright volt accents on the tongue, heel tab, and around the Swoosh add a dash of unexpected color to this military-inspired colorway.

name: Nike KD VI " Away "
description: EXCLUSIVE!!! KD continues to keep us on the tips of our toes with straight FIRE continuously releasing week after week.  Cop now!

name: Nike KD VI " Maryland Blue Crab "
description: Honoring his home of Maryland and his own appetite for the state’s renowned blue crabs, Kevin Durant and Nike‘s design team present a “Maryland Blue Crab” edition of Durant’s signature Nike KD VI. Inspired by the crab feasts KD would frequent throughout his childhood, kicks come reminiscent of the crab itself thanks to exact Pantone hues to match those of the crabs’ legs and pinchers – not to mention a shell-like textured effect throughout the upper. The theme is even transported to the shoe’s outsole as legs and pinchers adorn the usual holographic “KD” logo

name: Kamikaze " letter of intent"/ rainforest
description: Inspired by Shawn Kemp’s original commitment to the University of Kentucky, Wildcat blue and white make up the Reebok Kamikaze II “Letter of Intent”. As a McDonald’s All-American, Kemp chose to go to Lexington and be a part of one of the most storied programs in the country. Due to some academic complications, the thunder-dunking forward was forced to transfer to Trinity Valley Community College, where he only stayed for one semester before he entered his name into the NBA draft. This colorway of the Kamikaze II pays homage to the opportunity cost of UK. Do not sleep on these rainforest inspired color way as well
